description: Associates a Route 53 Profiles profile with a VPC. A VPC can have only one Profile associated with it, but a Profile can be associated with 1000 of VPCs (and you can request a higher quota). For more information, see https://docs.aws.amazon.com/Route53/latest/DeveloperGuide/DNSLimitations.html#limits-api-entities.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: A list of the tag keys and values that you want to identify the Profile association. (dict) --- Tag for the Profile. Key associated with the Tag. Value for the Tag.

nested_items.name: ProfileAssociation
nested_items.description: The association that you just created. The association has an ID that you can use to identify it in other requests, like update and delete.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the Profile association was created, in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

nested_items.name: ModificationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the Profile association was modified, in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

nested_items.name: OwnerId
nested_items.description: Amazon Web Services account ID of the Profile association owner.

nested_items.name: ResourceId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the VPC.

nested_items.name: StatusMessage
nested_items.description: Additional information about the Profile association.
